# Company profile

The official picture of this company. Structured data the orchestrator
and any collaborator should be able to consult to understand who we
are and what we're building.

This file is **instance property** — owned by the company, never
overwritten by `/sync`. Update by hand as the company evolves.

> **What goes here.** Mission, products, leadership, mottos / brand
> pillars, current strategic direction. The picture a new hire,
> investor, advisor, or collaborator needs to understand the company.
>
> **What doesn't.** Half-baked thoughts (those go in
> [`company-notes.md`](company-notes.md)). Stack specifics (those
> live in [`stack/`](stack/)). People roles + on-call (those live in
> [`ownership.md`](ownership.md)). Vendor specifics (those live in
> [`vendors.md`](vendors.md)). Long-arc tech vision (that's
> [`tech-vision.md`](tech-vision.md)).

